Havent been active for while, but now decided complete some of my old projects. This is first beta of my first trikz map. more levels will be added in later versions.

These first levels are around low-mid, later versions new levels will be propably mid-pro.

Give feedback to effect maps further progress.

Note; couldnt pack particles corectly so added them in folder. If someone knows how pack particles, please tell.

add 


particles_manifest
{
"file"		"particles/combine_fx.pcf"
"file"		"particles/tubes.pcf"
}

to your cstrike/particles/particles_manifest if particles arent otherwise visible.
